caption.text:
listen... I say this with love:

Please stop spending time creating Canva graphics for your IG Stories!

Stories are supposed to be in-the-moment, documentary, and authentic.

Stories are where we go to get connected with you on a deeper level.

Beautiful, premade graphics are often generic, lack personality, and just feel overdone.

Instead, create your Stories right in Insta! It's quicker and easier that way too!

caption.text:
🎤 Please Welcome Our Next Guest Speaker:
Instagram Growth Coach
Brock @brock11johnson 

👑 The unofficial “King of Reels”, has grown his Instagram by 1,000 followers per day over the past two years. From less than 70,00 to over 700,000.

🏉 Played Division 1 college football 

🐶 ⛰️ This Jesus lover, his beautiful wife and 2 dogs can often be found adventuring and exploring new places together. 

🎙️🎧 Co host of “Build Your Tribe” a Top 10 marketing podcast. 

💻He’s helped 1,000’s of entrepreneurs learn to use reels to connect and build their businesses 

🎤 He’s spoken on stages across the country

🎯 His mission is to help brands grow their following and effectively market using social media. 

🚀 Brock will be speaking at IGNITE Digital, an online summit hosted by Anneke @pinksparrowsocial 

28 Expert speakers - This September 1st-3rd

With replay access included. 

➡️ His Topic:

🔥🧨 How to create 50 posts in less than 1 hour.

➡️ You’ll learn:

💥 A system for content creation 

👇👇Comment “BROCK11” to learn more

🧨………… 💥 

Let’s Ignite your online income potential!

#ignitedigitalsummit #instagramgrowthexpert
